class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無人叫你同佢講你返四個月就走架嘛豬閪咁蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359fcabf651036d7365a965f40072aadc76a745a","tid":104203,"uid":2141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T04:16:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n大多數唔請 或者睇你有幾pt法<br />\n如果一星期兩三日就預咗byebye<br />\n佢呢個post係要返幾長時間下 因為唔夠人</blockquote><br />\n巴打 vet assistant 點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係咪即係「清理便便員」？</blockquote><br />\n要執下便便 餵下佢哋食嘢<br />\n但唔好忘記 愛協除咗貓狗 仲會有蛇/兔仔同其他動物<br />\n加上嚟得愛協嘅動物 大多數畀人遺棄 你要有好多心機同佢哋建立關係"},{"pid":"e0b92d0f40e1a3c88a16471ea451590de13c950e","tid":104203,"uid":82257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T04:23:05.000Z","msg":"我都想第時可以做啲同動物有關ge工<br />\n利申：讀緊marketing <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a9c3ee3f272648c9880ae2511adbbd9fdba8d1","tid":104203,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T04:53:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n巴打 vet assistant 點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係咪即係「清理便便員」？</blockquote><br />\n要執下便便 餵下佢哋食嘢<br />\n但唔好忘記 愛協除咗貓狗 仲會有蛇/兔仔同其他動物<br />\n加上嚟得愛協嘅動物 大多數畀人遺棄 你要有好多心機同佢哋建立關係</blockquote><br />\n依個唔係動物照顧員？<br />\n定係Vet assistant同動物照顧員工作差唔多？"},{"pid":"b55a9e3bf3ac9a53b09f0393d39298de1929747c","tid":104203,"uid":26823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T20:10:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想第時可以做啲同動物有關ge工<br />\n利申：讀緊marketing <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係marketing 咁岩既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cda8bb132d89ca901f5c975d2d81814ab39d679","tid":104203,"uid":26823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T20:11:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>見到佢有請動物照顧員想去做<br />\n但佢官網淨係寫左請full time<br />\n想知part time會唔會請？因為仲讀緊書 <br />\n如果開左學就返唔到full time<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但又好想做d同動物有關既工</blockquote><br />\n大多數唔請 或者睇你有幾pt法<br />\n如果一星期兩三日就預咗byebye<br />\n佢呢個post係要返幾長時間下 因為唔夠人</blockquote><br />\n如果返到4個月full time請唔請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無人叫你同佢講你返四個月就走架嘛豬閪咁蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我仲讀緊書佢實知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea3c9c98b52fcb82f4f310b8f38768128d57d5f9","tid":104203,"uid":2141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T16:52:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n巴打 vet assistant 點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係咪即係「清理便便員」？</blockquote><br />\n要執下便便 餵下佢哋食嘢<br />\n但唔好忘記 愛協除咗貓狗 仲會有蛇/兔仔同其他動物<br />\n加上嚟得愛協嘅動物 大多數畀人遺棄 你要有好多心機同佢哋建立關係</blockquote><br />\n依個唔係動物照顧員？<br />\n定係Vet assistant同動物照顧員工作差唔多？</blockquote><br />\nSorry我睇錯<br />\nvet assistant其實做嘅嘢會複雜啲嘅 同埋愛協總部(灣仔嗰間)啲獸醫鬼佬多 所以英文要有返咁上下 <br />\nvet assistant你可以當好似診所助護咁啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n動物照顧員對象就動物多 但有時都要同想領養嘅人解釋下動物嘅資料 例如點解動物畀人遺棄/有冇咩病咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你返工日子可以試下同佢傾 嗰陣我做另一個部門 原本話一星期返五日 但我返學 佢就畀我返少啲 可能我部門唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acbcaf4ed8e7c3a0624bff1e3d86a830cad22dcc","tid":104203,"uid":85431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T17:20:59.000Z","msg":"想入SPCA做,<br />\n自己有修過Animal Welfare既課程<br />\n但英文唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d64d9cda2d248015b6e4533c0917431be9f22cc9","tid":104203,"uid":57025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T10:26:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n大多數唔請 或者睇你有幾pt法<br />\n如果一星期兩三日就預咗byebye<br />\n佢呢個post係要返幾長時間下 因為唔夠人</blockquote><br />\n巴打 vet assistant 點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係咪即係「清理便便員」？</blockquote><br />\n要執下便便 餵下佢哋食嘢<br />\n但唔好忘記 愛協除咗貓狗 仲會有蛇/兔仔同其他動物<br />\n加上嚟得愛協嘅動物 大多數畀人遺棄 你要有好多心機同佢哋建立關係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n建立完，就會o拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}